  "texts": [
    "At the first stage in LLM integration, AI will be used as a tool to assist clinical providers and researchers with tasks that can easily be \"offloaded\" to AI assistants (Table 1; first row).",
    "As this is a preliminary step in integration, relevant tasks will be low-level, concrete, and circumscribed, such that they present a low level of risk.",
    "Examples of tasks could include assisting with collecting information for patient intakes or assessment, providing basic Fig.",
    "| Stages of integrating large language models into psychotherapy.",
